  <brief_title>Octreotide Acetate in Microspheres in Patients With Diabetic Retinopathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Controlled Study on the Efficacy and Safety of Octreotide Acetate in Microspheres in the Therapy of Patients With Moderately Severe or Severe Non-proliferate Diabetic Retinopathy (NPDR) or Low Risk Proliferative Diabetic Retinopathy (PDR)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
